data.description: Great opportunity to make this 4 bedroom, 1.5 bath home your new home! This home is located in the Cherry Acres neighborhood in Hampton, VA! When entering the home you will be greeted with a roomy living area which adjoins the dining room and kitchen. The primary bedroom with half bath is located to the rear of the home off the dining area. The other 3 bedrooms and full bathroom are located down the hallway. The kitchen has beautiful oak cabinets and all appliances will stay! This home has hardwood floors and ceramic tile in the kitchen and bathrooms. The backyard is fenced with a large deck to enjoy. Close to downtown Hampton and an easy commute to shopping centers, universities and all that the Hampton community provides for fun and entertainment. Make your appointment today!
